• A targeted, in-depth analysis of the baseline situation and needs;
• An updated report on the partnership and co-financing opportunities for the proposed project;
• Explicit specification of all capacity development activities to be financed under the project;
• A detailed breakdown of the project strategy using the Logical Framework Approach (log frame); 
• A detailed monitoring and evaluation plan for the project that builds upon the log frame;
• A stakeholder participation plan; 
